"""Test is_contextual method returns expected result."""
self.assertEqual(Compound(names=['Coumarin 343']).is_contextual, False)
self.assertEqual(Compound(melting_points=[MeltingPoint(value='240')]).
    is_contextual, False)
self.assertEqual(Compound(melting_points=[MeltingPoint(units='K')]).
    is_contextual, True)
self.assertEqual(Compound(melting_points=[MeltingPoint(apparatus=
    'Some apparatus')]).is_contextual, True)
self.assertEqual(Compound(labels=['3a'], melting_points=[MeltingPoint(
    apparatus='Some apparatus')]).is_contextual, False)
self.assertEqual(Compound(uvvis_spectra=[UvvisSpectrum(apparatus=
    'Some apparatus')]).is_contextual, True)
self.assertEqual(Compound(uvvis_spectra=[UvvisSpectrum(peaks=[UvvisPeak(
    value='378')])]).is_contextual, False)
self.assertEqual(Compound(uvvis_spectra=[UvvisSpectrum(peaks=[UvvisPeak(
    units='nm')])]).is_contextual, True)
